    <p>Whether you’re a student looking for a stay or a host listing your property, we’re here to help you get started smoothly.</p>

    <h4>Frequently Asked Questions:</h4>
    <ol>
        <li>How do I find accommodations near my college?</li>
        <p>Enter your college name or location in the search bar to view nearby verified listings.</p>

        <li>How do I contact a host?</li>
        <p>Click the “Contact Host” button on a listing you can message them directly through Accommate.</p>

        <li>How do I list my property?</li>
        <p>Go to the “List Property” page, fill out the details, upload images, and publish your listing instantly.</p>

        <li>Is Accommate free to use?</li>
        <p>Yes! Students can browse and connect with hosts for free.</p>
    </ol>
